002.perseus-grc1:8:389\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.389</biblScope> </bibl>: or c.<mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅν κ᾽ ἐπιεικὲς ἀκουέμεν</foreign> whom it may be <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">meet</tr_> for you to hear, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:547\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.547</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὅπλα . . οἷ᾽ ἐπιεικὲς ἔργ᾽ ἔμεν ἀθανάτων</foreign> such as is <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">meet</tr_> they should be, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:19:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.21</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.50</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:207\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.207</biblScope></bibl>. </sense><sense n=\"II\" id=\"n39331.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. after <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, </sense><sense n=\"1\" id=\"n39331.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. of statements, rights, etc., </sense><sense n=\"a\" id=\"n39331.3\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\">. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">reasonable</tr_>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">specious</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ δὲ τρίτη τῶν ὁδῶν πολλὸν ἐπιεικεστάτη ἐοῦσα μάλιστα</foreign> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIfo